108
00:10:13,446 --> 00:10:14,530
I like it.

109
00:12:09,011 --> 00:12:10,437
Oh, Nathan!

110
00:12:13,566 --> 00:12:14,775
Oh, Nathan.

111
00:12:21,324 --> 00:12:22,825
Oh, God!

112
00:12:31,835 --> 00:12:35,212
Don't you see, Sophie?
