You're going to have a picnic out
and down by the seashore.

117
00:12:55,525 --> 00:12:56,984
Good morning, Stingo.

118
00:12:57,068 --> 00:12:58,068
Good morning.

119
00:12:59,112 --> 00:13:02,406
We wanted to make friends

120
00:13:02,490 --> 00:13:05,200
and to take you out
on this beautiful summer day!

121
00:13:05,285 --> 00:13:07,828
We want you to come up
and have breakfast with us.

122
00:13:07,912 --> 00:13:09,204
- And then...
